title: JetBrains IntelliJ IDEA 14 Keygen
description:
Keygen for JetBrains IntelliJ IDEA 14 Ultimate.

Verified on Linux and Windows, though I'm sure it works on Mac OS too.

This is a minor modification of the IntelliJ IDEA 13 keygen that I posted at http://thepiratebay.se/torrent/9313672/JetBrains_IntelliJ_IDEA_13_Keygen -- changing the "version" byte to 14 is all that was required.

This keygen is a command-line Java program (package-less .class file) with source code. I compiled the source code with javac from Oracle JDK 8u25 on 64-bit Linux. If you have trouble running this on a different OS or want to be sure that the .class file matches the source code, feel free to recompile it yourself
